    "The student might help that character assess alternatives, weigh the pros and cons of different actions, and encourage the character to make well-informed decisions.",
    "In this case, the student would adapt to the context but \"play\" themselves in the scenario, incorporating the framework they learned in class.",
    "Importantly, in a goal play scenario the AI sets up a scenario in which the student knows something the character in the simulation does not and guides the character using what they know, generally a framework.",
